point : it be important to remember that the catholic church believe that barrier contraception be against god and that use it will condemn people to hell . therefore , even if the church's stance on condom be harmful , which the proposition do not accept that it be , it be less harmful than people spend an eternity suffering . in this context , therefore , the most responsible thing for the catholic church to do be to forbid the use of condom and , thereby , save people from hell1 . 1 pope paul vi . humanae vitae . 1968 . 4 
